    <h2>SurrealQL</h2>
    <p>SurrealQL is a powerful database query language which closely resembles traditional SQL, but with slight differences and improvements. Although it has similar syntax and similar statement types, there are a number of differences between traditional SQL and SurrealQL. </p>
